snippet.title: SORROW  - EEK3 Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Initially revealed during EEK3 2022 , SORROW is a "Survival Horror RPG" created for the Haunted PS1 community.
Inspired by games like King's Field, Bloodborne, and Silent Hill.
SITE - SorrowRpg.carrd.co
